Information

Jeremy Clarkson, Richard Hammond and James May are dropped deep in the Bolivian rainforest armed only with three shabby 4x4s, which they bought from the local small ads for a maximum of Â£3,500 each.

But before all that, they've got to escape from the deep, dark centre of the rainforest.
